cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Distil, please cite it."
title: "Distil: compression with a quality contract"
abstract: >-
  Cache-aware, causally-pruned context compression for agentic runtimes, gated by
  a statistical non-inferiority test. Reframes lossless compression as
  decision-equivalence and certifies it across a multi-domain trajectory corpus.
authors:
  - family-names: shakes
    email: chandu1221@gmail.com
repository-code: "https://github.com/dshakes/distil"
license: Apache-2.0
version: 0.18.0
keywords:
  - llm
  - context-compression
  - prompt-caching
  - agentic-runtime
  - non-inferiority
